                <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ios Phil<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> and my partner Aurelia Klodia, we acquired spotless land, firmly laid the foundation and made a grave for ourselves and for our heirs, and we declare that<gap reason="lost" extent="unknwon" unit="character"/></p>
